item.title: What I've Been Up To
item.description: My goal with this website was to document and share everything that I learn related to programming and technology. If you look around, it’s obvious that I haven’t done much of that since I started this site in May of 2017. I haven’t posted or done a thing since January of last year. So in an effort to get things back swinging here, I decided to make a quick post about what I’ve been up to in my technical life for the last year and 4 months.
